      <h4 class="sans-h4">
  
    
      <a href="/multimedia/daily-podcast/vipr-teams-execute-brazen-warrantless-searches">VIPR Teams Execute Brazen Warrantless Searches</a>
      </h4>
  

      <p class="mega-authors">
  
    
      <a href="/people/patrick-g-eddington" typeof="foaf:Person" property="foaf:name" rel="foaf:publications" html="1">Patrick G. Eddington</a>
      </p>
  

      <p class="text-sans">
  
    
      <span class="date-display-single" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2015-02-18T16:33:00-05:00">February 18, 2015</span>
      </p>
  
        
      <div>
  
    
      <a href="/multimedia/media-highlights-radio/william-poole-discusses-fomc-bloomberg-radios-hays-advantage"><picture >
